WEBVTT

00:07.600 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.840 --> 01:42.960
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.880 --> 01:47.600
‎XIE RESIDENCE

01:47.680 --> 01:49.400
Xie Yanlai needs someone to wait on.

01:50.320 --> 01:52.040
Does it really need
so many of us waiting here?

01:52.120 --> 01:54.080
Yeah. Who does he think he is?

01:54.160 --> 01:55.000
Alright, alright.

01:55.680 --> 01:56.520
It's the head's order.

02:04.720 --> 02:05.960
What's going on?

02:06.040 --> 02:07.280
What are they doing?

02:14.520 --> 02:17.000
Xie Yanlai, what do you think
you're doing?

02:17.080 --> 02:18.920
Yeah. What's your problem?

02:21.080 --> 02:23.080
Who gave you the nerve
to talk to me like that?

02:34.760 --> 02:35.800
Say it again.

02:36.480 --> 02:39.040
Don't think you can bully me
because you're in power.

02:39.120 --> 02:40.560
Yeah.

02:40.640 --> 02:41.560
That's right.

02:41.640 --> 02:42.880
But bullying the weak

02:44.040 --> 02:45.440
is what you do best.

02:45.520 --> 02:48.680
Our clan doesn't accept
a worthless lad like you.

02:48.760 --> 02:50.440
Since you're the son of a courtesan,

02:50.520 --> 02:52.320
then smile like her. Smile!

03:00.400 --> 03:03.880
He's said to be more powerful
even than Young Master Yanfang.

03:03.960 --> 03:05.760
Now, he's the Imperial Guard Commander.

03:05.840 --> 03:07.600
The Grand Princess appointed him.

03:07.680 --> 03:08.560
With power,

03:08.640 --> 03:10.920
he may revenge
for his childhood grievances.

03:11.440 --> 03:14.160
Young Master,
by Young Master Yanfang's orders,

03:14.680 --> 03:16.400
your house has been made ready.

03:16.480 --> 03:17.440
I'll take you there.

03:18.440 --> 03:20.160
-Go ahead.
-Yes.

03:36.280 --> 03:37.120
Father!

03:37.960 --> 03:39.320
Father!

04:02.160 --> 04:04.520
<i>Xie Yanfang is waiting to take advantage.</i>

04:05.040 --> 04:06.640
<i>Deng Yi is waiting</i>
<i>to profit from others' fight.</i>

04:08.400 --> 04:10.120
<i>Yet I have no idea</i>

04:10.200 --> 04:12.160
<i>about Father's physical condition.</i>

04:13.920 --> 04:15.840
<i>In my past life, as I recall,</i>

04:15.920 --> 04:18.120
<i>Father wasn't ill at this time.</i>

04:18.760 --> 04:21.079
<i>After my wedding,</i>
<i>the poisoned jujube cakes</i>

04:21.160 --> 04:22.920
<i>worsened his health.</i>

04:24.200 --> 04:26.200
<i>Did I neglect anything?</i>

04:30.520 --> 04:32.160
Your Highness, have some water.

04:41.400 --> 04:43.080
Your Highness, don't worry.

04:43.160 --> 04:44.320
Let me divine for you.

05:02.680 --> 05:03.640
It's all right.

05:04.160 --> 05:05.600
The crack points to the east.

05:05.680 --> 05:06.600
It's…

05:06.680 --> 05:08.320
an omen of misfortune
turning into fortune.

05:08.400 --> 05:10.240
Misfortune turning into fortune?

05:12.080 --> 05:14.160
So, misfortune comes first.

05:17.560 --> 05:20.840
Le, go send a letter to Chu Tang.

05:21.360 --> 05:23.000
Then have someone come to see me.

05:31.720 --> 05:34.120
Thank you for coming with me tonight.

05:34.200 --> 05:35.640
Take them to buy some drinks.

05:44.440 --> 05:45.600
Mr. Xie.

05:48.400 --> 05:49.240
Her Highness summoned you.

05:51.680 --> 05:52.640
<i>I'm going back to Yunzhong.</i>

05:53.920 --> 05:55.400
Do you know the consequences

05:56.280 --> 05:57.720
of leaving here without permission?

05:58.560 --> 05:59.640
I do.

06:00.680 --> 06:02.560
Deng Yi and Xie Yanfang
will get suspicious.

06:03.520 --> 06:06.480
When Le traveled around,
she met many Taoist physicians

06:06.560 --> 06:07.520
and got a prescription.

06:08.200 --> 06:09.560
Take it, and I'll faint from a high fever.

06:09.640 --> 06:10.680
My pulse will seem seriously weak.

06:11.360 --> 06:13.800
Then, Yu will give an order

06:13.880 --> 06:15.040
that nobody shall visit me.

06:16.840 --> 06:18.560
I won't let anyone disturb you.

06:25.200 --> 06:27.120
Le, take His Majesty to rest.

06:27.960 --> 06:28.840
Yes, Your Highness.

06:34.440 --> 06:36.440
If I feign illness and stay indoors,

06:36.520 --> 06:38.400
it'll just work out
in the ministers' favor.

06:39.160 --> 06:42.240
No one will verify if I'm truly ill.

06:42.320 --> 06:43.760
This is what they wish to see.

06:43.840 --> 06:46.120
How long can you hide this from those two?

06:46.840 --> 06:48.800
And Xiao Xun is back in his prefecture.

06:49.840 --> 06:51.200
If he gets to know about it,

06:52.240 --> 06:54.200
he won't allow you
to return to the frontier.

06:58.280 --> 06:59.320
Have you

07:00.640 --> 07:01.560
thought about all this?

07:03.320 --> 07:04.440
I have.

07:06.520 --> 07:08.200
Just because Xiao Xun is away…

07:12.640 --> 07:13.800
then I can leave.

07:16.360 --> 07:17.480
Since you stay in the court,

07:18.920 --> 07:20.600
I want to make it a quick trip.

07:24.400 --> 07:25.240
Jiu,

07:26.360 --> 07:27.480
help me.

07:40.440 --> 07:42.480
In the dream I told you about,

07:47.240 --> 07:49.000
my father was covered in blood.

07:52.880 --> 07:55.560
I want to make sure
my father is doing well.

07:59.760 --> 08:01.360
I have a lot of things

08:03.720 --> 08:04.840
to say to him.

08:06.360 --> 08:08.120
I don't want to have regrets

08:09.120 --> 08:10.080
in the future.

08:12.160 --> 08:13.960
You know how it feels when regrets

08:15.160 --> 08:16.360
can never be mended.

08:17.720 --> 08:18.880
Right?

08:44.000 --> 08:45.120
I'm still worried.

08:46.480 --> 08:47.440
You know…

08:49.320 --> 08:50.520
you can't stop me.

08:56.200 --> 09:01.640
CAPITAL

09:11.520 --> 09:13.720
Since when have you been so indecisive?

09:14.800 --> 09:16.600
You've escorted me over 30 li.

09:17.200 --> 09:19.760
Don't tell me you hate to part with me.

09:33.000 --> 09:34.080
Rest assured.

09:34.160 --> 09:35.760
My martial arts are mediocre,

09:36.280 --> 09:37.680
but I do practice every day.

09:40.200 --> 09:42.920
Your martial skills are no match

09:43.440 --> 09:44.360
for real masters.

09:47.720 --> 09:49.400
You wretched woman!

09:49.480 --> 09:51.120
Where do you think you can run to?

09:51.200 --> 09:53.520
I gave you food and drink,

09:53.600 --> 09:56.000
but you eloped with a man, didn't you?

09:56.080 --> 09:57.560
I'll break your legs!

10:04.080 --> 10:05.080
Spare my life, sir.

10:05.680 --> 10:07.800
I mistook you for someone else.

10:08.360 --> 10:13.000
Your carriage looks so much
like the one I'm looking for.

10:13.080 --> 10:15.240
I didn't recognize you

10:15.320 --> 10:16.880
and then offended you.

10:17.480 --> 10:18.680
Mistook us?

10:18.760 --> 10:21.200
Who are you really after?

10:21.280 --> 10:23.320
I run a pleasure house in Wuyang Town.

10:23.400 --> 10:24.880
My top courtesan

10:24.960 --> 10:27.160
ran off with a scholar
who went to the Capital.

10:27.240 --> 10:29.360
I came here to catch her.

10:29.960 --> 10:32.000
Unexpectedly, I stopped
the wrong carriage.

10:32.600 --> 10:34.040
I beg you to let me go.

10:34.120 --> 10:35.440
I don't want to die.

10:36.040 --> 10:36.960
Stop pretending.

10:37.680 --> 10:39.000
Who sent you?

10:39.520 --> 10:40.600
No one sent me.

10:40.680 --> 10:42.280
No one, really.

10:42.360 --> 10:44.080
I just got the wrong person.

10:44.160 --> 10:47.560
I don't want to die. Don't kill me.

10:50.480 --> 10:52.640
She doesn't seem to be lying.

10:53.800 --> 10:54.880
You may leave.

10:55.880 --> 10:57.280
Oh, thank you.

10:58.040 --> 10:59.280
Let's go.

11:04.040 --> 11:06.000
You're just like your father
in this aspect.

11:07.160 --> 11:08.720
You're both too trusting.

11:08.800 --> 11:09.920
When I was 14,

11:10.000 --> 11:12.160
I rode alone from Yunzhong to the Capital.

11:12.240 --> 11:13.800
I can tell good people from bad.

11:15.120 --> 11:16.320
I get it.

11:16.400 --> 11:17.600
But sometimes you can't.

11:18.120 --> 11:19.080
For example…

11:19.760 --> 11:20.840
Xiao Xun.

11:24.560 --> 11:25.680
Well, you're right.

11:26.200 --> 11:27.840
So what if I misjudged him?

11:28.360 --> 11:29.920
I fixed things, anyway.

11:30.760 --> 11:31.840
And I believe

11:32.800 --> 11:34.520
you won't let me get it wrong twice.

11:47.440 --> 11:48.440
Take this.

11:48.960 --> 11:50.160
Remember what I taught you.

11:52.760 --> 11:55.440
Didn't you say
my martial arts were useless?

11:57.080 --> 11:59.000
It's all right. I'm good at strategies.

12:06.440 --> 12:07.280
And this…

12:08.000 --> 12:09.240
You take it.

12:09.320 --> 12:11.200
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

12:11.800 --> 12:16.240
Do you know what
the Grand Princess Token means?

12:16.320 --> 12:17.600
It means

12:19.520 --> 12:20.360
I trust you.

12:30.000 --> 12:31.440
I'll keep it for now.

12:33.440 --> 12:34.520
And guard Yu for me.

12:37.400 --> 12:38.520
You…

12:41.240 --> 12:42.520
You take care.

13:00.640 --> 13:01.960
It's dark and far.

13:02.840 --> 13:04.160
Have a safe trip.

13:41.800 --> 13:44.960
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

13:49.840 --> 13:54.040
<i>Do you know what</i>
<i>the Grand Princess Token means?</i>

13:54.640 --> 13:55.760
<i>It means</i>

13:56.560 --> 13:57.600
<i>I trust you.</i>

14:15.680 --> 14:17.680
Your Highness, we got the news.

14:17.760 --> 14:19.320
Yesterday, the Grand Princess fell ill,

14:19.400 --> 14:20.600
had a fever, and skipped court.

14:28.600 --> 14:29.840
What a coincidence.

14:30.440 --> 14:31.680
Urgent news from Yunzhong

14:32.560 --> 14:34.080
said Chu Ling was gravely ill.

14:36.400 --> 14:38.960
I never expected the two of them

14:39.040 --> 14:40.840
to be so closely connected.

14:41.440 --> 14:42.880
If she left last night,

14:42.960 --> 14:44.520
I guess she's no longer in the Capital.

14:45.760 --> 14:47.840
Since she's out of town,

14:49.120 --> 14:50.320
I'll never let her go back.

14:51.320 --> 14:55.640
She'll pass through Wuyang Town
to Yunzhong.

14:55.720 --> 14:57.000
You…

14:57.080 --> 14:58.960
Have your men ambush outside town.

14:59.040 --> 15:00.680
Make sure that nothing goes wrong.

15:01.960 --> 15:03.000
I'm on it.

15:14.520 --> 15:15.760
Zhao.

15:23.200 --> 15:24.240
Stop the carriage.

15:28.560 --> 15:29.720
Where are we now?

15:29.800 --> 15:32.400
In half a day, we'll hit Wuyang Town.
Wait a minute.

15:32.480 --> 15:35.080
I'll hitch the horse
and tighten the reins.

15:35.960 --> 15:37.400
<i>As far as I know about Xiao Xun,</i>

15:37.920 --> 15:42.040
<i>he will make a move</i>
<i>upon receiving word of my illness.</i>

15:42.120 --> 15:44.000
<i>His men must be searching the town.</i>

15:44.600 --> 15:46.480
<i>This carriage is far too conspicuous.</i>

15:46.560 --> 15:47.400
<i>That's not safe.</i>

15:49.480 --> 15:51.000
Drop me off ten li outside the town

15:51.080 --> 15:53.440
and you go northwest
along the official road.

15:53.520 --> 15:55.040
Remember. You must not stop.

15:55.840 --> 15:56.960
All right.

16:05.360 --> 16:08.040
WUYANG TOWN

16:21.720 --> 16:22.840
<i>Just as I expected.</i>

16:22.920 --> 16:25.840
TEA

16:29.360 --> 16:30.600
Madam,

16:31.160 --> 16:32.960
those men don't look like good folks.

16:33.040 --> 16:34.320
What are they?

16:34.400 --> 16:35.600
Bandits?

16:36.120 --> 16:37.800
Don't say that.

16:37.880 --> 16:40.280
Our town has never
been plagued by bandits.

16:40.920 --> 16:43.120
They are the guards of a squire.

16:43.200 --> 16:46.040
I've heard a maid
stole valuables and ran off.

16:46.120 --> 16:47.400
Searching for a maid?

16:47.480 --> 16:48.720
Exactly.

16:48.800 --> 16:51.000
Their leader is really fierce.

16:51.080 --> 16:52.520
He even lifts up the veil
of the ladies' hats.

16:55.040 --> 16:56.560
Madam, get me some tea.

16:57.160 --> 16:58.160
Coming.

17:17.240 --> 17:18.200
Mr. Deng,

17:18.280 --> 17:20.240
Her Highness is resting.
She won't see anyone.

17:20.319 --> 17:22.640
Her illness involves the court.

17:22.720 --> 17:24.720
It's my duty to check on her.

17:25.520 --> 17:26.720
Don't you dare disobey me.

17:28.040 --> 17:28.880
How daring!

17:28.960 --> 17:31.280
You have no authority
over the inner palace.

17:32.000 --> 17:32.920
Take one more step forward

17:33.560 --> 17:34.520
and my sword

17:35.360 --> 17:36.240
won't show mercy.

17:43.160 --> 17:44.160
Good.

17:45.360 --> 17:46.400
Very good.

17:47.040 --> 17:48.040
Mr. Xie,

17:48.920 --> 17:50.680
let's wait and see.

18:10.480 --> 18:11.680
For her,

18:13.240 --> 18:14.480
you even offended Deng Yi.

18:17.120 --> 18:18.240
It is merely my duty.

18:19.440 --> 18:20.480
Far from offending.

18:22.560 --> 18:24.280
Tie Ying left Xiaonan

18:24.800 --> 18:26.560
and laid ambushes all the way to Yunzhong.

18:27.960 --> 18:28.800
Do you really think

18:29.720 --> 18:30.920
she can reach the frontier alive?

18:32.320 --> 18:34.480
She's stronger than you think.

18:39.560 --> 18:42.440
Right. She's exceptionally smart.

18:43.080 --> 18:45.920
But even if she can survive
Xiao Xun's ambushes,

18:46.720 --> 18:48.600
she has forgotten something.

18:50.240 --> 18:52.600
Bandits run rampant
along the way to the frontier.

18:53.640 --> 18:55.440
I'm afraid other dangers

18:56.760 --> 18:58.320
are lying ahead for her.

19:00.280 --> 19:02.040
She's a woman, after all.

19:02.120 --> 19:04.640
If she happens to run into those outlaws,

19:05.240 --> 19:06.440
how many miles

19:07.560 --> 19:09.400
do you think she can survive?

19:11.360 --> 19:12.400
Yanlai,

19:12.960 --> 19:15.200
guard the imperial city well.

19:15.800 --> 19:18.320
Otherwise, when the news
of her death comes,

19:19.880 --> 19:21.920
no one will hold a funeral for her.

19:34.480 --> 19:35.760
You wretched woman!

19:35.840 --> 19:37.240
You ran away one by one.

19:37.320 --> 19:39.680
Why? Didn't I feed you
or buy you nice clothes?

19:39.760 --> 19:42.120
I bought you with 20 liang of silver!

19:42.200 --> 19:44.320
If you just… Watch where you're going!

19:49.760 --> 19:50.600
We meet again.

19:55.720 --> 19:56.840
Move aside.

19:57.880 --> 19:59.960
My Lord, carriage tracks northwest.

20:00.040 --> 20:01.280
It has special horseshoe markings,

20:01.360 --> 20:02.920
like those of the Capital.

20:03.000 --> 20:04.280
Report!

20:05.320 --> 20:06.920
Behind the north dune, we found this,

20:07.000 --> 20:08.960
with "Zhao" on it.
I think it's from a noble lady.

20:10.240 --> 20:12.200
Report!

20:12.280 --> 20:13.880
Northeast, a woman hired a guard escort

20:13.960 --> 20:15.160
to send her to the frontier.

20:15.240 --> 20:16.560
She splurged a lot.

20:17.680 --> 20:18.920
Three traces.

20:19.760 --> 20:21.040
She left false clues, huh?

20:22.040 --> 20:23.360
Pass my order.

20:23.440 --> 20:26.000
Go three ways.
Northwest, north, and northeast.

20:26.080 --> 20:27.600
Pursue all of them.

20:27.680 --> 20:30.560
My Lord, if we pursue rashly, I'm afraid…

20:30.640 --> 20:32.320
Better kill the innocent than let them go.

20:32.920 --> 20:35.040
Every suspicious woman must be arrested.

20:35.120 --> 20:36.240
Yes.

20:44.640 --> 20:47.800
BEICAO POST HOUSE

20:49.320 --> 20:50.160
It is good.

20:50.240 --> 20:52.040
-The beef tastes good.
-Postmaster,

20:52.120 --> 20:53.800
the post house is small,

20:53.880 --> 20:55.280
but you offer very good service.

20:55.360 --> 20:57.000
You deliver messages to Yunzhong.

20:57.080 --> 20:58.360
The journey must be rough.

20:58.440 --> 21:00.160
This post house is just like a home.

21:00.240 --> 21:01.680
Right? You deserve nice food.

21:03.320 --> 21:05.880
Who is this girl? She isn't a local, huh?

21:06.480 --> 21:07.840
She's a poor girl.

21:08.360 --> 21:10.040
Her father worked at the frontier.

21:10.120 --> 21:12.360
She and her mother
came all the way for him.

21:12.440 --> 21:13.720
Sadly, on their way,

21:13.800 --> 21:15.880
her mother fell gravely ill.

21:15.960 --> 21:17.560
Obviously, she's going to…

21:18.760 --> 21:20.800
Officers, please take me to Yunzhong.

21:21.840 --> 21:24.680
-I want to see my father.
-But…

21:25.640 --> 21:27.640
It's urgent news. We must not delay.

21:27.720 --> 21:29.320
Officers, this girl is sensible.

21:29.400 --> 21:31.320
During the trip, she won't bring trouble.

21:31.400 --> 21:33.720
There in Yunzhong,
General Chu commands strictly.

21:33.800 --> 21:35.600
When he knows you've helped someone,

21:35.680 --> 21:37.760
maybe you'll be given credit for this.

21:37.840 --> 21:38.800
What do you think?

21:41.920 --> 21:44.400
We're dispatch riders from Wangcheng Camp.

21:44.480 --> 21:47.160
We've met General Chu a few times.

21:47.960 --> 21:49.120
Head up.

21:51.760 --> 21:53.520
There are many troops at the frontier.

21:54.040 --> 21:55.960
Tell me your name and background.

21:56.560 --> 21:58.480
-She is--
-Let her speak.

22:02.080 --> 22:03.560
My name is Fu.

22:04.160 --> 22:06.000
My father is Yang Dachun.

22:06.880 --> 22:10.120
He serves at Saishang Outpost
in Daqing Mountain Camp,

22:10.200 --> 22:12.000
under General Chu Ling's command.

22:16.200 --> 22:18.120
This is my father's letter.

22:22.600 --> 22:23.880
His handwriting is good.

22:36.280 --> 22:37.480
Take us to see your mother.

22:37.560 --> 22:39.480
If you're telling the truth,

22:39.560 --> 22:40.720
we'll take you along.

22:41.880 --> 22:43.400
Get up. Come on.

22:44.560 --> 22:45.480
I'll take you to see her.

22:47.320 --> 22:48.720
Mother. Mother.

22:48.800 --> 22:50.640
Some officers will head for Father's camp.

22:50.720 --> 22:53.160
Mother. Mother. Mother.

22:54.400 --> 22:55.360
Mother.

22:58.120 --> 22:59.280
Mother.

23:01.320 --> 23:02.600
Have some water.

23:05.720 --> 23:06.880
Officers,

23:07.400 --> 23:10.000
are you heading for Daqing Mountain Camp?

23:10.080 --> 23:11.280
No.

23:11.800 --> 23:12.840
But we'll pass by.

23:14.840 --> 23:17.920
What's your husband's name?

23:18.440 --> 23:19.280
How old is he?

23:20.200 --> 23:21.400
Who does he work for?

23:22.760 --> 23:25.000
-You asked just now.
-Let her answer.

23:32.160 --> 23:33.200
My husband…

23:35.360 --> 23:36.360
is Yang Dachun.

23:37.440 --> 23:38.880
The seventh day of the third month.

23:39.400 --> 23:41.080
He serves under General Chu.

23:43.840 --> 23:45.280
Mother. Mother.

23:45.960 --> 23:46.840
I…

23:48.360 --> 23:49.360
I made him…

23:50.000 --> 23:51.080
a pair of new shoes.

23:52.520 --> 23:53.360
Fu,

23:54.440 --> 23:55.880
promise me you will

23:56.400 --> 23:59.000
give the shoes to your father.

24:04.040 --> 24:05.520
Let me be blunt.

24:06.040 --> 24:07.800
Our mission is urgent.

24:07.880 --> 24:09.320
The journey will be tough and swift.

24:09.400 --> 24:10.760
Young girl,

24:11.280 --> 24:13.480
keep up if you can.

24:13.560 --> 24:16.120
If you can't, we'll leave you behind.

24:17.080 --> 24:18.440
Officers,

24:18.520 --> 24:21.360
take her as far as you can.

24:22.160 --> 24:24.880
The closer she gets to her father,

24:24.960 --> 24:29.200
the sooner her father will find her.

24:29.960 --> 24:32.880
Fu, kowtow and thank them.

24:34.760 --> 24:36.160
Thank you, officers.

24:37.760 --> 24:38.640
Mother.

24:41.440 --> 24:42.680
-Enough.
-Mother.

24:42.760 --> 24:44.440
Tomorrow morning, we'll set off.

24:46.920 --> 24:48.320
Officers!

24:49.360 --> 24:52.560
If you manage to see my husband,

24:52.640 --> 24:54.800
please tell him

24:54.880 --> 24:57.960
I am blessed
to be his wife all these years.

24:58.960 --> 25:00.720
My life is worth it.

25:01.480 --> 25:02.720
Mother.

25:05.920 --> 25:08.760
Life is so hard. So hard.

25:09.360 --> 25:10.760
My poor girl.

25:12.600 --> 25:13.560
Get packed.

25:13.640 --> 25:15.840
Our schedule is fixed.
We can't stay too long.

25:18.040 --> 25:19.120
This way.

25:20.120 --> 25:22.960
Life is so cruel to us!

25:23.680 --> 25:26.720
Oh, so cruel.

25:28.600 --> 25:30.480
So cruel.

25:39.720 --> 25:42.440
Is there a girl who has my figure?

25:43.920 --> 25:45.560
Oh, I see.

25:45.640 --> 25:48.920
So you want a substitute.

25:50.880 --> 25:51.760
That's hard.

25:52.360 --> 25:53.360
Look at you.

25:53.440 --> 25:55.760
You're slender and tall.

25:55.840 --> 25:58.440
Ordinary girls
wouldn't be as great as you.

25:59.720 --> 26:01.840
There are. As many as you want.

26:03.400 --> 26:04.920
Then, do you have children?

26:07.680 --> 26:10.160
Just now, why did you add something extra?

26:12.440 --> 26:14.320
I'm "dying".

26:14.400 --> 26:16.680
When I missed your father
and recalled our old days,

26:16.760 --> 26:21.280
that was natural, uncontrollable,
and touching.

26:21.800 --> 26:23.000
You're too young.

26:23.080 --> 26:24.520
When it comes to love,

26:24.600 --> 26:26.480
I'm more experienced, after all.

26:26.560 --> 26:29.240
A frontier soldier's wife
wouldn't speak such sentimental words.

26:34.880 --> 26:36.600
Fine. It's my fault. Come on.

26:37.520 --> 26:40.760
Tomorrow, will you really
follow those riders?

26:41.280 --> 26:42.240
Will they see through you?

26:42.320 --> 26:43.760
Of course I will.

26:46.480 --> 26:48.720
Because I've noticed their secret.

26:50.040 --> 26:50.880
What secret?

26:54.800 --> 26:56.800
XIE RESIDENCE

27:12.920 --> 27:16.480
Yanlai, why do you act like a thief
in your own home?

27:17.200 --> 27:18.520
I have a favor to ask.

27:20.520 --> 27:21.360
Keep it between us.

27:22.280 --> 27:23.960
How strange.

27:24.560 --> 27:27.600
I never thought you would ask for a favor.

27:31.840 --> 27:32.800
Help me leave the Capital.

27:34.840 --> 27:36.640
As the Imperial Guard Commander,

27:37.640 --> 27:38.920
you mustn't desert your post.

27:39.880 --> 27:40.960
It's the rule.

27:41.680 --> 27:43.000
You know it better than me.

27:43.680 --> 27:44.880
You're right.

27:46.040 --> 27:47.880
The trip to Yunzhong is very dangerous.

27:48.920 --> 27:50.560
She holds a unique status.

27:50.640 --> 27:51.760
If anything happens…

27:53.400 --> 27:54.320
Yanlai,

27:55.440 --> 27:57.240
I've never seen you

27:58.800 --> 28:00.280
care about someone like this.

28:07.280 --> 28:09.400
The Grand Princess affords
to feign illness.

28:10.040 --> 28:12.040
It's not easy for you

28:12.720 --> 28:14.400
to leave.

28:16.360 --> 28:17.600
Have you thought it through?

28:23.840 --> 28:24.920
If you help me,

28:27.600 --> 28:29.000
I'll owe you one.

28:39.160 --> 28:41.200
Food and water bags are ready.

28:41.280 --> 28:42.600
Take care.

28:43.200 --> 28:44.400
Thank you.

28:44.480 --> 28:46.360
And I'll trouble you
to take care of my mother.

28:46.440 --> 28:47.640
BEICAO POST HOUSE

28:47.720 --> 28:48.840
Count on me.

29:02.720 --> 29:04.360
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

29:05.480 --> 29:06.720
Stop playing.

29:06.800 --> 29:08.400
You haven't finished your lessons.

29:08.480 --> 29:10.120
If the Grand Mentor finds out…

29:11.440 --> 29:12.880
Leave me alone.

29:13.680 --> 29:17.280
If you still nag, I'll order you
to catch a hundred crickets.

29:22.640 --> 29:23.760
Why aren't you studying?

29:28.080 --> 29:29.160
Uncle, you're just in time.

29:29.760 --> 29:32.080
Look. The cricket in my cage

29:32.160 --> 29:33.600
is far funnier than the Analects.

29:34.560 --> 29:35.520
Your Majesty,

29:36.800 --> 29:39.800
the Imperial Study is no place for fun.

29:44.000 --> 29:45.000
How dare you throw away my cricket!

29:47.240 --> 29:48.240
Your Majesty.

29:48.320 --> 29:50.320
Xie Yanlai, how daring!
You pushed me over!

29:51.840 --> 29:52.960
Your Majesty.

29:53.480 --> 29:54.920
Mr. Xie, how could you do this?

29:56.960 --> 29:59.400
Commander Xie Yanlai misbehaved

29:59.480 --> 30:01.280
and pushed His Majesty over.

30:01.360 --> 30:03.200
This is blatant disrespect.

30:03.280 --> 30:06.120
If such behavior is allowed,
all rules will be gone.

30:06.200 --> 30:08.040
You're exaggerating, Mr. Deng.

30:08.680 --> 30:10.200
My brother has been respectful.

30:10.280 --> 30:12.400
He serves His Majesty devotedly.

30:13.000 --> 30:14.440
His Majesty is young and playful.

30:14.520 --> 30:18.920
Maybe as they played around,
my brother just slipped up.

30:19.000 --> 30:20.800
Are you suggesting

30:21.400 --> 30:24.520
His Majesty is slandering a minister?

30:24.600 --> 30:25.600
How dare I?

30:25.680 --> 30:28.960
The Imperial Guard Commander
secures the imperial city.

30:29.040 --> 30:31.560
If he's punished for stopping His Majesty

30:31.640 --> 30:32.760
from playing too much,

30:33.360 --> 30:35.800
the soldiers will be disheartened.

30:35.880 --> 30:37.480
You really defend your brother.

30:38.160 --> 30:40.560
The Grand Princess has been absent.

30:40.640 --> 30:42.400
The Imperial Guards are so arrogant.

30:43.000 --> 30:44.840
Mr. Xie, do you think

30:44.920 --> 30:46.840
there is no restraint

30:47.360 --> 30:48.880
for the court?

30:51.960 --> 30:53.680
Don't drag Her Highness into this.

30:54.360 --> 30:55.560
She hasn't recovered yet.

30:55.640 --> 30:58.880
His Majesty cares for her
and grants her a quiet recovery.

30:59.480 --> 31:00.720
As for the restraint…

31:01.520 --> 31:03.400
You govern for His Majesty.

31:03.480 --> 31:05.360
Isn't it the greatest restraint?

31:05.440 --> 31:06.640
Enough!

31:07.880 --> 31:09.840
Xie Yanlai disrespected me!

31:09.920 --> 31:11.600
He'll be suspended for reflection!

31:11.680 --> 31:12.720
Grand Mentor!

31:13.600 --> 31:15.040
Draft the edict for me.

31:15.560 --> 31:16.920
How wise, Your Majesty.

31:17.520 --> 31:19.480
The Imperial Guards need a leader.

31:19.560 --> 31:21.080
I recommend

31:21.600 --> 31:24.160
-the deputy commander to fill in.
-Don't bother.

31:24.760 --> 31:26.040
I'll select candidates

31:26.560 --> 31:28.760
to handle Imperial Guard affairs.

31:28.840 --> 31:30.840
His Majesty will decide.

31:30.920 --> 31:34.080
Just do it as you wish.
I'm tired. Court is dismissed!

31:35.440 --> 31:38.160
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty.
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty.

31:58.000 --> 31:58.760
‎TAIJI HALL

31:58.840 --> 32:00.560
<i>Fu Jiu, the Imperial Guard Commander,</i>

32:00.640 --> 32:01.960
<i>offended His Majesty.</i>

32:02.040 --> 32:05.160
<i>He got suspended from post.</i>

32:12.280 --> 32:13.320
Yanlai.

32:13.400 --> 32:14.360
ONE DAY AGO

32:14.440 --> 32:16.440
His Majesty wants this letter
to Her Highness.

32:17.120 --> 32:18.360
I'm quite curious.

32:18.880 --> 32:20.960
How has the Grand Princess fascinated you?

32:24.960 --> 32:26.240
Over the past five years,

32:29.640 --> 32:30.800
I never owed anyone.

32:30.880 --> 32:33.280
Do you trust me with Yu just like that?

32:34.080 --> 32:36.360
In the imperial city,
many fierce forces are lurking.

32:39.400 --> 32:41.040
He can only be entrusted to you.

32:42.560 --> 32:43.840
He's of Xie Family's bloodline

32:44.600 --> 32:46.120
and your own nephew.

32:49.840 --> 32:51.160
Then give me

32:51.960 --> 32:53.240
the Grand Princess Token.

32:55.360 --> 32:56.680
If she trusts you,

32:57.920 --> 32:58.760
she must have given it.

33:02.080 --> 33:03.600
The enemy is before us.

33:05.080 --> 33:06.840
You should know what matters most.

33:07.960 --> 33:09.840
Now, the court is ruled by three forces.

33:10.560 --> 33:12.200
Deng Yi drafts edicts.

33:12.280 --> 33:13.600
I review the edicts.

33:14.200 --> 33:17.040
Without the Grand Princess's approval,
no ministries shall seal them.

33:18.000 --> 33:19.120
I give you my word.

33:19.200 --> 33:21.560
I will protect Yu at any cost.

33:22.800 --> 33:24.520
I know what worries you.

33:25.720 --> 33:27.280
But don't forget.

33:27.880 --> 33:31.000
The Token can only stop Deng Yi
from issuing unauthorized edicts.

33:32.200 --> 33:33.080
It has no other use.

33:33.960 --> 33:35.840
Even if I have a plan with it,

33:35.920 --> 33:38.280
I won't succeed
without Deng Yi's Imperial Seal.

33:39.760 --> 33:40.880
The token will just

33:40.960 --> 33:42.960
make it easier to counterbalance

33:43.040 --> 33:44.280
Deng Yi and me.

33:45.240 --> 33:47.600
So, Yanlai, don't doubt my intentions.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.680
Besides,

33:50.280 --> 33:51.840
with nothing to trade,

33:51.920 --> 33:54.960
how could I willingly agree to your terms?

34:13.760 --> 34:15.320
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

34:15.400 --> 34:17.600
CAPITAL

34:34.800 --> 34:37.800
Xie Yanlai, the pawn, is out of the game,

34:37.880 --> 34:41.639
leaving the state to you and Xie Yanfang.

34:43.080 --> 34:46.360
Aren't you going
to set up a scheme of loyalty

34:46.440 --> 34:47.920
when the emperor's still young?

34:49.000 --> 34:50.239
When Xiao Yu was little,

34:50.920 --> 34:52.400
he was badly frightened.

34:53.040 --> 34:54.199
Once the crowd grows,

34:54.280 --> 34:56.280
he always hides behind Chu Zhao.

34:59.000 --> 35:00.200
Wait.

35:01.880 --> 35:03.240
Chu Zhao has left.

35:03.320 --> 35:04.560
Xie Yanlai is suspended.

35:05.600 --> 35:07.240
What's in it for Xie Yanfang?

35:09.040 --> 35:11.000
In today's court,

35:11.520 --> 35:13.160
he seemed happy about that.

35:16.840 --> 35:18.400
You're really something, Xie Yanfang.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.280
Only now have I realized

35:20.800 --> 35:23.440
that you used me to complete your game.

35:24.000 --> 35:28.240
Is he plotting something
against the emperor?

35:28.840 --> 35:30.000
It doesn't matter.

35:31.400 --> 35:33.920
Xie Yanfang is an uncle in name only.

35:34.640 --> 35:36.440
His Majesty is distant from him.

35:36.520 --> 35:37.720
They won't get close.

35:37.800 --> 35:40.200
What if he makes the first move

35:41.160 --> 35:42.880
to catch us off guard?

35:44.800 --> 35:45.960
Don't worry.

35:46.480 --> 35:47.720
He dare not act rashly.

35:49.040 --> 35:50.880
After all, in the court game,

35:52.280 --> 35:53.720
we like to seize the initiative

35:56.960 --> 35:57.880
and fear making a misstep.

35:57.960 --> 35:59.280
However,

36:00.280 --> 36:01.880
if Chu Ling dies,

36:02.400 --> 36:04.280
Northern Desert soldiers
will march straight here.

36:04.360 --> 36:05.640
By then,

36:06.360 --> 36:09.400
neither you nor the Xie Family
can get away without losses.

36:09.920 --> 36:11.200
You're right.

36:11.960 --> 36:13.200
So, in this game,

36:13.720 --> 36:15.680
we're not sure what we'll do next.

36:16.200 --> 36:17.800
But we both know

36:19.280 --> 36:21.320
that Chu Ling must not die now.

36:31.120 --> 36:33.000
Xie Yanlai left town
at the first quarter of the Shen hour.

36:33.080 --> 36:35.560
He rode your favorite Dark Steed.

36:35.640 --> 36:37.040
Calculated by speed,

36:37.120 --> 36:39.720
he must have reached Beicao Town.

36:39.800 --> 36:41.440
He was quite obedient.

36:41.960 --> 36:43.640
He didn't even suspect

36:43.720 --> 36:45.320
the horse I gave him.

36:45.400 --> 36:46.840
How would he?

36:46.920 --> 36:48.800
You gave him your best horse.

36:48.880 --> 36:49.960
He should be grateful.

36:51.280 --> 36:53.160
Well, he was sensible this time.

36:53.760 --> 36:55.560
He did give you the Token.

36:57.480 --> 36:59.640
This token isn't of much use.

37:00.240 --> 37:01.600
But it works very well

37:02.120 --> 37:03.720
to trouble Deng Yi.

37:03.800 --> 37:04.880
But

37:04.960 --> 37:08.000
Xie Yanlai obviously has got feelings
for the Grand Princess.

37:08.080 --> 37:09.560
Do you think

37:10.160 --> 37:11.560
he'll get more out of our control?

37:15.960 --> 37:17.760
The best part of taming a baby wolf

37:18.280 --> 37:21.200
is to make it think
it has broken free from the collar.

37:22.120 --> 37:24.840
Actually, the collar
was replaced with gold cord.

37:25.520 --> 37:27.120
The harder he struggles,

37:27.640 --> 37:28.960
the tighter it binds him.

37:29.640 --> 37:32.000
He's risking his life to save Chu Zhao.

37:32.640 --> 37:34.480
He thinks he's resisting.

37:35.560 --> 37:38.320
Actually, he has revealed
his fatal weakness.

37:39.480 --> 37:41.280
He once told me

37:42.400 --> 37:43.800
Chu Zhao was very clever.

37:45.680 --> 37:48.760
I thought he lost his judgment,
driven by emotions.

37:52.200 --> 37:55.160
That woman behaves so clumsily
and anxiously.

37:57.920 --> 37:59.600
What makes her smart?

38:00.680 --> 38:02.480
Now I finally understand.

38:04.200 --> 38:05.680
Making Yanlai care so much about her

38:06.960 --> 38:09.360
proves her great wisdom.

38:14.080 --> 38:15.640
How foolish of me.

38:17.480 --> 38:18.480
I fail to realize…

38:18.560 --> 38:19.400
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

38:20.000 --> 38:22.320
…your subtle schemes.
